p://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9955995406679284, \"rank\": 0.004417889154859725, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 383, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matt Richardson, Australia's three-time Olympic medallist, has announced his switch to the British cycling team.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9729824523843779, \"rank\": 0.02776771737606382, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The move marks a significant new chapter in the 25-year-old's career as he returns to his roots in the UK.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996540230349512, \"rank\": 0.00034609334543564066, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He brings with him a wealth of experience and a recent string of successes.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson, who was born in Maidstone, Kent, before relocating to Western Australia at the age of nine, has made headlines for his impressive performances at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidstone\", \"score\": 0.9996766404998324, \"rank\": 0.00032346409541218323, \"text\": \"Maidstone\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidstone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidstone\"}, {\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent\", \"score\": 0.9999999526189651, \"rank\": 4.738003741707269e-08, \"text\": \"Kent\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Games, he clinched silver medals in both the individual sprint and keirin events, alongside a bronze in the team sprint, according toThe Guardian.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His decision to join Great Britain's cycling team comes after much deliberation and is now officially sanctioned by the Union Cycliste Internationale (UCI).\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998393044324088, \"rank\": 0.00015074160178506644, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9382831471983348, \"rank\": 0.06577636278815499, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.9999999999899956, \"rank\": 9.799590664303538e-12, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have made the decision to pack up my entire life and move halfway across the world to begin the next chapter in my cycling career,\\\" Richardson declared.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is with a sense of excitement and renewal that I announce I have joined the Great British Cycling Team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson's move reflects a deep personal commitment to pursue his passion under new guidance, according toBBC.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will now train under Sir Jason Kenny, one of Britain's most decorated cyclists.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jason Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Kenny\"}, {\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9974271898695235, \"rank\": 0.002571435878222398, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is known for his unparalleled success on the track.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson's change of nationality is not just a strategic career move but also a heartfelt return to his birthplace.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1716, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It marks a poignant moment in his professional journey.\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson acknowledged the complexity of the choice.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recognised the respect and gratitude he holds for Australia and the Australian Cycling Team, according toSky News.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9729824523843779, \"rank\": 0.02776771737606382, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9955995406679284, \"rank\": 0.004417889154859725, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999836495591, \"rank\": 8.30761726971729e-09, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Switching nationality was a difficult decision and not one I took lightly,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a personal choice, made after careful consideration of my career and future.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I deeply respect Australia and the Aus Cycling Team, and it will always be a part of who I am.\\\"\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9729824523843779, \"rank\": 0.02776771737606382, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999836495591, \"rank\": 8.30761726971729e-09, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matt Richardson emphasised that this move is not about leaving behind his past but rather embracing a new beginning.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2335, \"end\": 2350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is not about leaving something behind, but about embracing a new chapter in my journey and chasing a dream.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A dream that is to race for the country where I was born,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Matt Richardson's accomplishments in recent years are nothing short of impressive.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is a doublegold medalistfrom the 2022 Commonwealth Games and has earned five world championship medals.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This included a gold in the 2022 team sprint.\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His career trajectory has been on an upward curve, making him a valuable addition to the British team as they look to bolster their competitive edge on the international stage.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2969, \"end\": 2976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9989697678865103, \"rank\": 0.0006688519385061514, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As he prepares to settle back in the UK, Matt Richardson's transition is likely to invigorate the British cycling team.\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3095, \"end\": 3097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996540230349512, \"rank\": 0.00034609334543564066, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3099, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 3156, \"end\": 3171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The synergy between his past achievements and the expertise of his new coaches could well set the stage for future triumphs.\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the backing of Sir Jason Kenny and the support of a familiar home environment, Richardson's journey promises to be an exciting one.\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3329, \"end\": 3340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jason Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Kenny\"}, {\"begin\": 3389, \"end\": 3399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the coming months, cycling enthusiasts and analysts alike will be watching closely to see how Richardson adapts to his new role.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3540, \"end\": 3550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999869855857, \"rank\": 1.3014297516695022e-08, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His story is a testament to the dynamic nature of international sport and the personal sacrifices athletes make in pursuit of their dreams.\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or by emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.comor sending a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3830, \"end\": 3838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.6566082277813032, \"rank\": 0.5229781743355253, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor the latest news.\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 4025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3946, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9995191620602064, \"rank\": 0.0004810381530480506, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 3950, \"end\": 3952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_R